      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im having some really bad pain in my stomach... it started right by my belly button a few hours ago but now it moved down to the lower right side and it's super sharp. i think it might just be bad gas or maybe really bad cramps from my period? i really need to sleep though so is it okay if i take some extra strong ibuprofen or maybe even some codeine to help it go away so i can rest?",
